```query MyQuery {
  HUBDB {
    careers(uniqueIdentifier: "", uniqueIdentifierValue: "") {
      hs_child_table_id
      hs_created_at
      hs_name
      hs_path
      hs_updated_at
      teams
    }
  }
}```
